<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link crossorigin="anonymous" rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/about.css">
    <title>YuruCamp</title>
</head>

<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">

    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
        <header class="mb-auto">
            <div>
                <h3 class="float-md-left mb-0">&#9651;YuruCamp</h3>
                <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-right">
                    <a class="nav-link " aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link active">About</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/campgrounds">Campgrounds</a>
                    <% if(!currentUser) { %>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                            <% } %>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="px-3 mb-3">
            <div class="container mt-5">

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Welcome to &#9651;Yuru Camp</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Yuru Camp is a campground management project designed for outdoor enthusiasts who
                        want to explore, share, and discover beautiful camping spots. Inspired by the <em>Yuru Camp</em>
                        (Laid-Back Camp) series and modeled after the <em>YelpCamp</em> project, this platform provides
                        a simple and user-friendly interface for users to view and add campgrounds.</p>
                </section>

                <div class="row align-items-start">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                        <div class="section-content">
                            <h5 class="section-title">Our Mission</h5>
                            <p>Our mission is to create a vibrant community of camping lovers where everyone can find
                                their perfect getaway in nature. Whether you're searching for a serene lakeside retreat,
                                a mountain campsite, or a family-friendly location, Yuru Camp is here to help you
                                discover new outdoor adventures. We believe that camping is a wonderful way to connect
                                with nature, make lasting memories, and unwind from everyday life.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                        <div class="section-content">
                            <h5 class="section-title">What We Offer</h5>

                            <h6 class="section-subtitle">Explore Campgrounds</h6>
                            <p>Browse a curated list of campgrounds with detailed descriptions, photos, and user
                                reviews. Discover hidden gems and popular spots across various regions.</p>

                            <p>Check out this amazing <a href="https://www.japan-travel-note.com/tags/7"
                                    style="text-decoration: none;font-weight: bolder; color: aliceblue;" target="_blank"
                                    rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                    resource</a> which features <em>Yuru Camp</em> campgrounds from anime!</p>

                            <h6 class="section-subtitle">Add Your Favorite Campgrounds</h6>
                            <p>Share your camping experiences by adding your own campgrounds to the platform. Include
                                essential details like location, amenities, and tips to help fellow campers plan their
                                trips.</p>

                            <h6 class="section-subtitle">User Reviews and Ratings</h6>
                            <p>Read and contribute reviews to help others make informed decisions about their camping
                                destinations. Your insights can guide fellow adventurers in choosing the right
                                campground for their needs.</p>

                            <h6 class="section-subtitle">Responsive Design</h6>
                            <p>Enjoy a seamless experience on any device. Yuru Camp is built with responsiveness in
                                mind, ensuring that you can explore and add campgrounds whether you're on a smartphone,
                                tablet, or desktop.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                        <div class="section-content">
                            <h5 class="section-title">Join Us</h5>
                            <p>Become a part of the Yuru Camp community! Whether you're a seasoned camper or just
                                starting your outdoor journey, we invite you to explore our platform, share your
                                experiences, and connect with other camping enthusiasts.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-indicators">
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0"
                            class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1"
                            aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2"
                            aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="3"
                            aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkkzaekid/image/upload/v1734181370/inukoLBC2_qwlphz.jpg"
                                class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkkzaekid/image/upload/v1734157517/ousa_lbc_hero_bvfmdl.png"
                                class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkkzaekid/image/upload/v1734179815/wp3745668_olgb4h.jpg"
                                class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkkzaekid/image/upload/v1734179814/R_eov2wa.jpg"
                                class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
                        data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
                        data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>

        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy;&#9651;YuruCamp-2024 </p>
        </footer>


    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>